Introduction

Lee Seong-hwa, known as Gray (stylized as GRAY) is a South Korean singer, rapper and record producer.

He is the head producer at AOMG, and has collaborated with many artists, such as the likes of LOCO, Zion.T, Crucial Star, Hyolyn, ONE, Simon Dominic, Jay Park, Sleepy, Hoody, Ailee, Swings, Shinhwa, Ugly Duck, Sik-K, Dynamic Duo, Gaeko, G2, Elo, BewhY, WANNAONE...etc.

Gray debuted in 2012 and is currently signed to hip hop record label AOMG headed by Jay Park.

In 2016, he appeared as a judge on the reality television program Show Me the Money 5.
